{"tid":640328,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"燒鄧家彪議辦　泰婦監3年","createTime":"2018-04-24T08:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T11:25:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ae0c25d4e02ffa199a8b8b1d3734375a3426ce3f","tid":640328,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180424/20370801?_ga=2.35775392.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F20370801%3F_ga%3D2.35775392.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=6rgDRqZdkloq1MaO0jNX4wEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=3a7377df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F20370801%3F_ga%3D2.35775392.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=790552f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180424/20370801?_ga=2.35775392.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月24日 <br />\n<br />\n燒鄧家彪議辦　泰婦監3年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180424/large/a1205a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180424%2Flarge%2Fa1205a.jpg&h=c56c5816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄧家彪的議辦大門被燒毀。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】日兼兩職養家的泰裔港婦稱遭陌生男子當街指罵是「雞」，向當區區議員鄧家彪求助，要求找出該男子，惟鄧稱「非常難做，做唔到」，轉向鄰舍輔導會要求跟進又被拒，一怒之下連環於鄧的議員辦事處及鄰舍輔導會縱火洩憤。她早前在區院承認兩項縱火罪，昨被判囚3年。<br />\n<br />\n法官指兩罪性質嚴重，其中次罪提及被告Sunisa Wan（41歲）曾緊握門把以阻單位內職員離開，表現兇殘，罔顧有可能造成人命傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n案發去年10月2日國慶日補假下午，被告先在東涌逸東邨鄧的辦事處外放火，燒毀大門及膠簾，其後到邨內鄰舍輔導會綜合服務中心放火，幸火勢很快自行熄滅。<br />\n<br />\n辯方早前指生於泰國的被告嫁到香港，育有16歲女兒，3年前丈夫中風，被告要獨力養家，但從無怨言。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC1062/17<br />\n■記者蔡少玲  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n與男友虐打女兒　婦判感化"},{"pid":"196c6d0eaefe5cda05213ad058810185dad18e70","tid":640328,"uid":36077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:13:41.000Z","msg":"痛快"},{"pid":"cc0e3284982697d3402a5e8245c48535f8344dce","tid":640328,"uid":65346,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:13:46.000Z","msg":"因為無燒死陷家虎.... benz brake ! 要受3 look <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3eec7dde3d292ae6851a40b2a98f52c96938f4","tid":640328,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"扶不起的阿斗<br />\n佢仲有冇得撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f1c8b91e52d45d1216f2e0202d99e290a23956","tid":640328,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:31:17.000Z","msg":"可能學垃圾桶一樣！<br />\n失了義席，得一高薪官位！"},{"pid":"140e36119d37d72b587b8d65a1b6db93a3f3253c","tid":640328,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"最好燒埋樓主泛民打手LIKLN冚家<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/163240_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F163240_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=19c00937&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"250aa3510dc912de99d79a2da5daa7bd6fe406a3","tid":640328,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:22:33.000Z","msg":"表現兇殘? 只聽過手法兇殘"},{"pid":"c350fd1ed5a3cb0cf69ddc270fa6d0c20ab8b41f","tid":640328,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"南亞雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}